title: Establish a DAO budget channel or website where how much the DAO treasury holds is visible.
body: This would be a Discord channel supported by a bot or our website that gives full details about DAO balance and other items like the current projects we are working on and strategies we are taking to increase DAO funds. This way we all understand the tokenomics of the DAO and also think of ways to improve it and raise funds collectively.
author: 0xa11435b21e0Eff08A6c2c5b8316ACC94054e8bAB
